Birds featured in this book include: Eastern Bluebird, Evening Grosbeak, Bullfinch, Bohemian Waxwing, Superb Starling, Regent Bowerbird, Inca Jay, Gouldian Finch, Northern Cardinal, and Blue Jay.

Check out the other books in this trademarked series: Happy Day: A Bouquet in a Book, Thinking of You: A Bouquet in a Book, Succulents in a Book, and Party in a Book.',0,0,'290080','Earle, Lesley','Abrams Noterie','http://image.kyobobook.co.kr/images/book/xlarge/932/x9781419733932.jpg',null,to_date('19/02/05','RR/MM/DD'),'해외');
